(option "Players" <Player> args:{<count> <score> } 
 {
  (item "2" <2>  <> "Two players")
  
  (item "3" <3> 
   <(score P3 (value Player P3))>
   "For Multiplayer games, a player wins when they have:
 1. At least tied with a moving player that has no space left to expand, when both have more than their share of the board.
 2. Taking up at least half of the space available to the 2 largest players in the game.
 3. Has more than half the board.
 4. By score if there are no moves left.

 Three players")
   
  (item "4" <4> 
   <(score P3 (value Player P3)) (score P4 (value Player P4))>
   "For Multiplayer games, a player wins when they have:
 1. At least tied with a moving player that has no space left to expand, when both have more than their share of the board.
 2. Taking up at least half of the space available to the 2 largest players in the game.
 3. Has more than half the board.
 4. By score if there are no moves left.


  Four players")
 }
)

